<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.&nbsp;<br><br>Following our conversation, please find attached some information about our policy add-ons:</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Cyber Liability</b>&nbsp;– provides support and guidance if you’re hit by a cyber incident.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Legal Expenses</b>&nbsp;–&nbsp;protects your business in the event of legal action.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>IR35 Protect&nbsp;</b>–&nbsp;safeguards your business from costs following an IR35 enquiry.&nbsp;</font></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px;"></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you have any questions or wish to discuss these products in more detail, please give me a call on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br><br>Kind regards<span style="background-color: white;">,<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="background-color: white;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="background-color: white;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="background-color: white;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="background-color: white;">01242 808740</font></font></p>]]></td>
